        Download EnviousWispr Free
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="directory-line reveal" style="margin-top: 28px;">Want every head-to-head? See all <a href="/compare/">11 Mac dictation app comparisons</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
